With Women: Midwives experiences: site na ngbanwe ọrụ gaa n'ihu na nlekọta bụ akwụkwọ nke anọ sitere n'aka onye edemede Australia David Vernon.
Akwụkwọ a bụ akwụkwọ nchịkọta akụkọ nke ahụmahụ nke ụmụ nwaanyị ndị na-amụ nwa site n'inye nlekọta na gburugburu ọrụ mgbanwe gaa n'ịnye kulawa na ụdị nchebe
Ahụmahụ ndị akọwapụtara dịgasị iche, site na nkọwa nke mmegbu n'ebe ọrụ ruo omume onwe onye n'ime otu ìgwè na-arụkọ ụka.
Akwụkwọ ahụ nwere okwu mbido nke Sheila Kitzinger dere, Okwu mmalite site na Dr Sally Tracy, yana nkwubi ihe Justine Caines na Dokta Jenny Gamble dere.
